@startuml
actor User
participant Website
participant "Flask API" as FlaskAPI
participant APIFree

User -> Website: Submit travel preferences (form)
activate Website

Website -> FlaskAPI: POST /itinerary/create\n{preferences}
activate FlaskAPI

FlaskAPI -> APIFree: POST /generate\n{preferences, options}
activate APIFree

APIFree --> FlaskAPI: 200 OK\n{itinerary data, image URL/base64}
deactivate APIFree

FlaskAPI --> Website: 200 OK\n{itinerary, image}
deactivate FlaskAPI

Website --> User: Display generated itinerary and image
deactivate Website
@enduml